Gunspin is a physics game where you shoot a gun to keep it flying for as long as possible. Upgrade your gun with more bullets and power to make it travel even further.

How to Play
Fire your gun
Shoot your gun to the left and use all your bullets to send the gun flying as far as possible. Every metre you travel is a coin earned. The coins you earn can then be used to buy more bullets, power, and ammo boxes.

Unlock new guns
Each round you have the possibility of unlocking a new gun by reaching a distance milestone. The guns all have unique sounds and stats, so find one you prefer and use it to maximize your score!
